---
title: Easy As Kiwi Spiced Plant-Based Mince Tacos with Cucumber & Garlic Aioli
description: Taco night is always a winner in our books. Introducing our newest taste sensation - spiced plant-based mince, cooked until golden and tossed in honey for that sweet-and-savoury mix. Add crunch with a fresh slaw and cucumber and some creamy goodness from the garlic aioli. Pack the lot into a warm tortilla and enjoy!
